[[div class="jotting" style="max-width: 300px; margin: auto; font-style: italic;"]]
**__##red|LESSON##__**

IF TWO ONES MAKE TWO
AND ##blue|TWO TWOS## MAKE ##blue|FOUR##
WHAT'S TO DO WHEN ##blue|TWO TWOS##
WON'T MAKE ##blue|FOUR## ANYMORE

WHEN VALUES IN BASE TEN
RETURN SUMS IN BASE EIGHT
THAT TWO FOURS MAKE TEN
IS THE SUM OF ONE'S HATE

IF A EQUALS B
AND C IS NOT A
TO HEAR THAT B'S C
LEAVES ONE WROUGHT WITH DISMAY

WHEN THE ##blue|ENEMY## OF AN ##red|ENEMY##
IS THE ##blue|ENEMY## OF ONE'S ##green|FRIEND##
AND HOPE OF ANY CLARITY
YIELDS CHAOS IN THE END

SUCH IS A ##red|PUNISHMENT##
FOR ##blue|THOSE WHO WANDER##
TOO FAR FROM **##brown|THE PATH##**
OF **##green|THE FOREST WITHOUT NAME##**
AND SEEK ##red|KNOWLEDGE##
THAT IS BEST LEFT UNKNOWN

FOR THE CRIME OF NAMING
**##red|THAT WHICH OUGHT NOT BE NAMED##**
##blue|YOU## MUST ACCEPT THAT REALITY
__DOESN'T ALWAYS MAKE SENSE__

[[span class="bblock"]]**LOGICIAN**[[/span]]
[[/div]]

